00:49:03.874 --> 00:49:06.343 align:middle line:84%
And you're the first person
I've ever told this in my life,

00:49:06.343 --> 00:49:10.114 align:middle line:84%
but-- and then they would
come forth with these things.

00:49:10.114 --> 00:49:12.950 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Yes, and so once
you give permission and open

00:49:12.950 --> 00:49:15.586 align:middle line:84%
the room to a scientific
community-- but the fact

00:49:15.586 --> 00:49:18.155 align:middle line:84%
