all scientifically makes

00:49:18.155 --> 00:49:19.490 align:middle line:90%
such a huge difference.

00:49:19.490 --> 00:49:21.692 align:middle line:84%
>>DOSSEY: It makes a tremendous
amount of difference.

00:49:21.692 --> 00:49:24.762 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: For you, specifically,
and for the medical community.

00:49:24.762 --> 00:49:27.398 align:middle line:84%
>>DOSSEY: And the fact, in
that particular situation,

00:49:27.398 --> 00:49:31.368 align:middle line:84%
that I was willing to tell them
my premonitions, which I did,

00:49:31.368 --> 00:49:34.104 align:middle line:84%
