a fool out of myself,

00:49:34.104 --> 00:49:36.974 align:middle line:84%
gave them permission
to come forward

00:49:36.974 --> 00:49:39.443 align:middle line:84%
and say things to this
group that they had never

00:49:39.443 --> 00:49:41.178 align:middle line:90%
